```plantuml
@startuml oovk_dataengg-covid19-aws

actor User
participant "Jupyter Notebook" as Notebook
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "Pandas" as Pandas
participant "Amazon Redshift" as Redshift

User -> Notebook: Execute ETL pipeline
Notebook -> Athena: Query COVID-19 datasets
Athena --> Notebook: Return query results
Notebook -> S3: Store raw data
Notebook -> Pandas: Load data into DataFrames
Pandas --> Notebook: Return transformed DataFrames
Notebook -> Pandas: Perform data transformations
Notebook -> Pandas: Create dimensional model
Notebook -> S3: Store transformed data (CSV)
Notebook -> Redshift: Execute CREATE TABLE statements
Notebook -> Redshift: Load dimensional model data
Redshift --> Notebook: Confirm data load

@enduml
```